. [https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8491681/sia-new-album-feature-length-musical-2019 \"Sia Promises New Album, Feature Length Musical in 2019\"], '|-'[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'', December 28, 2018</ref>\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[To All the Boys: P.S. I Still Love You]]''\n| Cheerleader\n| Cameo\n|<ref>Ellman, Lucinda. [https://www.elitedaily.com/p/maddie-zieglers-cameo-in-to-all-the-boys-ps-i-still-love-you-is-everything-21799215 \"Maddie Ziegler's Cameo In ''To All The Boys: P.S. I Still Love You'' Is Everything'\"], ''Elite Daily'', February 12, 2020</ref>\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[West Side Story (2020 film)|West Side Story]]''\n| Velma\n| Post-production\n|<ref name=Sorren/>\n|}\n\n===Television===\n<!-- Please note: do NOT use \"rowspans\" per WP:FILMOGRAPHY -->\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+Key\n|-\n| style=\"background:#bdf;\"| {{*|alt=Acting credits of Maddie Ziegler}}\n| Denotes acting credits\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Network\n! Notes\n! {{Abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Live to Dance]]''\n| Herself\n| [[CBS]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|Episode did not air\n|<ref name=LiveToDance/>\n|-\n| 2011\u20132016\n| ''[[Dance Moms]]''\n| Herself\n| [[Lifetime (TV network)|Lifetime]]\n| Main cast, 162 episodes\n|<ref>Rosenbloom, Alli. [http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/maddie-ziegler-is-leaving-dance-moms-after-six-seasons-w159932 \"Maddie Ziegler Is Leaving Dance Moms After Season Six\"], ''US Weekly'', December 17, 2015</ref>\n|-\n| 2012\u20132015\n| ''[[The View (talk show)|The View]]''\n| Herself / Performer\n| [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]\n| 3 episodes\n|<ref>Kirsch, Megan. [http://www.dancespirit.com/news/abby-lee-miller-on-the-view/ \"Abby Lee Miller on 'The View'\"], Dance Spirit magazine, February 22, 2013</ref>\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Drop Dead Diva]]''{{*|alt=Acting credits of Ziegler}}\n| Young Deb\n| Lifetime\n| Episode: \"Lady Parts\"\n|<ref name=Screener/>\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Abby's